Map inspired by the game "Minecraft". Created with the source graphics engine for Counter-Strike Source.

=======objective=======

Trying to get to the center, to enter the portal, which will take you to choose the multiple games, which are:

Scout and Knife: typical scout and knife map. Kill the other team with Scout and Knife.

AWP: AWP typical map. Kill the other team with AWP.

Ice Skate: typical ice skate map. Kill the other team with Knife.

Race: typical race map. Run as fast as you can and overcoming all obstacles, to reach first and get the m249.

Bhop: typical bhop map. Jump as fast as possible, reach the end and get the m249.

Knife Battle: kill the other team with a single blow with the knife.

Random Weapons: Each round will be different, try to point you in the head.

Climb: Climb typical map. Upload as fast as you can without falling, and you will get the m249.

Train: Buy a gun, you have 10 seconds to do, and 3 seconds to hop on the train, which will go to full speed. Try to kill the other team, before they do so.

HE: HE typical map. If in 5 min not win, it will break the barrier.

Survive: Try to survive the fall of TNT, these will fall randomly, try to last longer than your opponent.

Zombie Attack: Try to survive the hordes coming at you from all sides, headshots, to kill and shooting in the arm to not get hurt. Care at the end, with the Enderman.

Break Glass: breaking vidro of where your opponent well, make him fall.

Diamon Search: search the entire mine diamonds in chests and in its raw form, when you get the 3 diamonds earn.

Strongholds: finds the portal to the end. in order to win.

Total: 15 minigames + 1 random for the undecided.

If there are errors, comment :).

Enjoy FuChuSS

Basically this is a small mg map of CTs vs Ts. Everyone will start outside (picture 1) and go into a cave and drop down a hole. You will fall into some lava and there will be a lever and some tnt. Hit the lever to make the tnt explode. After the tnt has exploded, there will be a teleport area and a small lava area with a nade (picture 2). The nade will make whoever grabs it half invisible. (lava will kill you). After 10 seconds of being teleported to a small black box, the map will randomly choose some settings. The map will choose the arena, gravity, hp, weapon, and song. Everyone will then be teleported to whichever arena and will kill eachother with whatever gun they got.

Hi all.


As you can see I have completed yet another Mario themed map (its a cool theme to work with!).

I will explain each area as best I can.

The Entrance
============
The entrance is a giant circular room with 16 question mark boxes in the middle. When players spawn, they must try and hit their heads on the boxes, attempting to find the correct box. When the correct box is selected, a mushroom will spawn and run away from the players (a physbox +thrusters) and a player must walk into the mushroom to be teleported to the selection room (above).

The boxes randomize each round so it will rarely be the same box that gets you in. If a player falls down or does not select a game, it will automatically select the game after 45 seconds from round start.


Hunger Games
============
This game mode usually turns a few heads (which is what we are going for) so we decided to add it. 

Players start in a pipe in the middle of the map.The countdown begins and the players are elevated above the pipe when the game begins.
There are 3 types of guns that spawn (randomised): deagle, dak dak and m3 shotty, as well as some knives. All guns only have clip ammo and no reloads.

When the game starts, players must find a gun on the map and kill each other to win.

Obstacle
========
This was my first attempt at an obstacle course, and I think it went well. It is hard to find the balance in obstacle - make it too easy and players complain, make it too hard and player complain more.

We built this obstacle to replicate the elements in Mario. Easy - Summer, Snow - intermediate, Desert - hard, Castle - very hard. You obviously start in summer and progress your way through creative obstacles in a race to the finish. First one to the end wins the match.

Skipping
========
This was the last minute mini game as most of the team dropped out of the project and I had to build something quickly. I am quite happy with how it turned out though.

There is a pillar in the middle with 2 propellers, 1 on each end. When the game starts, they will rotate around the pillar, moving up and down every 2 seconds. It gets incredibly challenging trying to predict the movement at high speeds.

This is the kind of game you will keep dying on, but it will be hilarious and make you want to come back for more.

Pirate Island
=============
This was a late addition to the map. It is located in the center of the pipe for selection.

It uses a targeting system that will select a random player on the island and target them with a giant boulder (physbox). As the game progresses, the boulders spawn more frequently and the island gets smaller and smaller. Knives spawn in the middle after a period of time to help end the round.

Hexagon Heat
============
I will do a write up for the old mini games as a lot of people havent played the JB map. Hexagon heat is a fun game involving multi colour platforms and a quick response time.

A colour is selected at random and displayed above the platform, and players must run to said colour as quickly as possible or they fall into the lava and die.
The game gets increasingly faster as more colours are selected, and if any do manage to survive, knives will spawn and players can knife fight while trying to keep their balance.

Platform peril
==============
Platform peril is the game you love to hate, and you hate to love. It is a race style game that proceeds up a series of platforms. 

As the game progresses, the platforms will begin to fall making it challenging to those left behind. There are a series of obstacles obstructing your way on the way up so you need to be quick but smart at the same time.

Pirate Climb
============
This is the same pirate climb from the secret minigame in the JB map. The only difference besides its automated start up, is the fact that 33% more boulders spawn now.

The objective of the game is to get to the top of the tower as quickly as possible while dodging the boulders. The first person to the top gets a cool mushroom hat to make them feel better - while everyone else dies.

There are also 2 sets of lasers that the player must maneuver around.

Mario Says
==========
This is my personal favorite. The game is similar to that of Simone says. It is based off the mini game "Shy guy says" but there are no shy guy models available so I decided to make it Mario says.

Players move themselves onto platforms in the map. After the allocated delay time, the floor will break and players will be trapped on their platform. Mario will begin to hold up a series of flags with letters or nothing on them.
Players must use their control buttons to do what Mario says. If you choose incorrectly, your platform descends into the water and you die.

The game requires quicker response times as it progresses.

MarioKart
=========
I have added a mario kart minigame with 20 karts available. Players must complete 3 laps of the course to win.

There are obstacles in the way and diamonds that the players can driver over to obtain turtle shells.

This game auto locks if more than 20 players are alive.

Conclusion
==========
I am very happy how the map turned out and I would like to thank all those involved in the process.

Please rate and leave feedback.

Enjoy!
